org.beryx.streamplify.permutation

Class LongPermutations

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.beryx.streamplify.LongIndexedSpliterator<int[],LongPermutations>
      • org.beryx.streamplify.permutation.LongPermutations
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Spliterator<int[]>, Streamable<int[],LongPermutations>

    public class LongPermutations
extends LongIndexedSpliterator<int[],LongPermutations>
    Provides streams of permutations.
    Can be used for permutations with a maximum length of 20. For bigger values, a BigIntegerPermutations is needed.
